						<summary>

						<p>Unfinished. It seems to record a gift by Mūtta Kuñjiramallaṉ, a resident of Kaṟkuḍi in Maḻanāḍu on the northern bank of Kāviri, to the temple of Śrī Pōndaipperumānaḍigaḷ, at Rājamallach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam at Tiruvēgambapuram in Dāmarkōṭṭam.</p>						

